{"tid":23242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[單親媽溺斃]痛失好媽媽 19歲女崩潰：好後悔冇盡囡嘅責任","createTime":"2016-12-04T22:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T23:43:06.000Z","uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"831618b585c8cc4ac47f72d4029885c7c627eda9","tid":23242,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xta1/v/t1.0-9/11743001_494314270717770_6648977926824262800_n.jpg?oh=8606db1b7a4e27b620a4c3d1fbfe5d79&amp;oe=5621258D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fhphotos-xta1%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F11743001_494314270717770_6648977926824262800_n.jpg%3Foh%3D8606db1b7a4e27b620a4c3d1fbfe5d79%26oe%3D5621258D&h=172c4231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「佢臨返工前都會游水，但今日出咗去就冇返過嚟！」42歲姓林女子上午於屯門蝴蝶灣泳灘溺斃，遺下現正就讀副學士課程的19歲姓馮獨女，陰陽相隔，女兒接受《蘋果》訪問時崩潰痛哭：「好掛住佢...」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者的丈夫6年前因糖尿病併發逝世，自始母兼父職，任機場保安員養家，獨力養大女兒。死者熱愛游泳，每日返工前必會到海灘游早水，惟今晨卻不幸遇溺，一去不返。愛女痛失雙親，孤苦無依，就連母親的殮葬費亦成問題，她回憶起母親多年來克勤克儉，為她供書教學，不禁自責：「佢好錫我，好想帶佢食好嘢，好後悔冇盡囡嘅責任！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20150717/53985378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20150717%2F53985378&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d86bf93c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20150717%2F53985378&h=a978f01c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20150717/53985378</a>"},{"pid":"a84324b4e36b6687787c073d5dbd38a393d27088","tid":23242,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/062615_8fa20965ddd46f1bfa6763c788c4237c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F062615_8fa20965ddd46f1bfa6763c788c4237c.jpg&h=12dc7dc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe7bd9a8ebce991201b9c5fdf1bef1aa11b400b4","tid":23242,"uid":1836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:31:44.000Z","msg":"19歲就雙失...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eddeb5fc0456bb0f3e4403b99c07732a9542a3c","tid":23242,"uid":23828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:33:09.000Z","msg":"一個人之後嘅路點行，佢會好徬徨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80efec6e282f2cfb48c0a030b7c725a4c758d35b","tid":23242,"uid":5521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:38:56.000Z","msg":"已經估計到下面啲留言"},{"pid":"f191c7ef32519714fbb8c8f18ccd123a418473bf","tid":23242,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經估計到下面啲留言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa70a91131357b72c3443bdefb3051b448e2fc94","tid":23242,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:41:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1291a896c86af1bc9d95bd62c5371f96b0c5cdb2","tid":23242,"uid":5521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已經估計到下面啲留言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n預咗㗎啦"},{"pid":"b45f1cde292a04fb18b73c5b8e419989dcd14191","tid":23242,"uid":1737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T22:52:42.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdcce8225b9c162b5241e3b14e46b52e1f42345","tid":23242,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T23:34:34.000Z","msg":"成年啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad60875b5c89e58ee525b1004f4652177f76854a","tid":